      "content": "You are not alone in feeling this hopelessness, and it is completely understandable to question every effort when the pain seems so permanent. However, the fact that you are still reaching out means there is a part of you that is still searching for a way out, even if the path feels invisible right now. True freedom often begins not by fighting the world, but by allowing yourself to exist without the pressure of being judged by it. Please consider reaching out to a mental health professional or a trusted friend who can help you navigate this darkness with support and hope. You deserve to feel peace, and it is possible to find it even in the deepest moments of struggle.",
